  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/b68ed76dd3801f713c25da3de5882b64.avif?t=1746200550\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras_big/b68ed76dd3801f713c25da3de5882b64.avif?t=1746200550 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the haunting world of <strong>Dark Honor</strong>, an action-packed game inspired by classic Souls-like titles. In this dark fantasy realm, you play as a lone warrior seeking vengeance against the fearsome Samurai tribe that has devastated your village and taken your family.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/3c93412a61a199b87549e3c36006e769.poster.avif?t=1746200550\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/3c93412a61a199b87549e3c36006e769.webm?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/3c93412a61a199b87549e3c36006e769.mp4?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features an advanced combat system that requires players to master skills and strategy. Prepare to face relentless enemies and engage in epic boss battles that will test your abilities and courage. Every fight demands focus and skill as you wield your sword with precision and utilize the environment to your advantage.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/45fa028e5383c9746dfb4da8d7b9830f.poster.avif?t=1746200550\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/45fa028e5383c9746dfb4da8d7b9830f.webm?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/45fa028e5383c9746dfb4da8d7b9830f.mp4?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore immersive environments, from abandoned villages to shadowy forests, each filled with secrets and peril. Throughout your journey, uncover the tragic history of this world and confront challenging obstacles that put your combat skills to the test.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With stunning visuals powered by Unreal Engine and an immersive soundtrack, <strong>Dark Honor</strong> offers a thrilling gaming experience filled with tension and excitement. Are you ready to confront the darkness and reclaim your destiny? Join the fight and embark on your quest for revenge!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/a47da27db1690e3086d93d588756ed61.poster.avif?t=1746200550\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/a47da27db1690e3086d93d588756ed61.webm?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/a47da27db1690e3086d93d588756ed61.mp4?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/b68ed76dd3801f713c25da3de5882b64.avif?t=1746200550\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras_big/b68ed76dd3801f713c25da3de5882b64.avif?t=1746200550 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the haunting world of <strong>Dark Honor</strong>, an action-packed game inspired by classic Souls-like titles. In this dark fantasy realm, you play as a lone warrior seeking vengeance against the fearsome Samurai tribe that has devastated your village and taken your family.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/3c93412a61a199b87549e3c36006e769.poster.avif?t=1746200550\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/3c93412a61a199b87549e3c36006e769.webm?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/3c93412a61a199b87549e3c36006e769.mp4?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features an advanced combat system that requires players to master skills and strategy. Prepare to face relentless enemies and engage in epic boss battles that will test your abilities and courage. Every fight demands focus and skill as you wield your sword with precision and utilize the environment to your advantage.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/45fa028e5383c9746dfb4da8d7b9830f.poster.avif?t=1746200550\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/45fa028e5383c9746dfb4da8d7b9830f.webm?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/45fa028e5383c9746dfb4da8d7b9830f.mp4?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore immersive environments, from abandoned villages to shadowy forests, each filled with secrets and peril. Throughout your journey, uncover the tragic history of this world and confront challenging obstacles that put your combat skills to the test.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With stunning visuals powered by Unreal Engine and an immersive soundtrack, <strong>Dark Honor</strong> offers a thrilling gaming experience filled with tension and excitement. Are you ready to confront the darkness and reclaim your destiny? Join the fight and embark on your quest for revenge!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/a47da27db1690e3086d93d588756ed61.poster.avif?t=1746200550\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/a47da27db1690e3086d93d588756ed61.webm?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331610/extras/a47da27db1690e3086d93d588756ed61.mp4?t=1746200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
